      "description": "## Install\n\nOnce approved in the Obsidian community directory, install Better Kanban Bases View from Settings > Community plugins.\n\nFor manual installation, download the release assets and place manifest.json, main.js, and styles.css in .obsidian/plugins/bases-kanban-view-ttvl/.\n\n## Highlights\n\n- Adds a Kanban Bases view for grouped notes.\n- Supports column and card reordering.\n- Supports selected Bases properties, formula values, and optional card previews.\n- Uses the plugin id bases-kanban-view-ttvl for community directory uniqueness.",
